thread.title: Kevin Dolan
thread.title_full: TAXIBOX mobile self-storage reviewed by Kevin Dolan

author: Kevin Dolan
title: Kevin Dolan
text:
Really great service. Everyone I dealt with was exceptionally helpful. Even after I mistakenly booked the Taxibox for too early in the morning, the team sorted it all out with no fuss.
Andrew, who delivered the boxes, was also very helpful and went above and beyond. He was not phased in the slightest by our awkward tiny streets. Really impressed.
Thanks guys!
